<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Green Leaf - Contact Us</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="pics/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/bd5c7c48a0.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@5.15.4/css/fontawesome.min.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 50px;
      line-height: 64px;
      color: #222;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 46px;
      line-height: 54px;
      color: #222;
    }

    h4 {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #222;
    }

    h6 {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 15px 0 20px 0;
      color: rgb(59, 54, 54);
      font-weight: 300;

      line-height: 22px;
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .section-p1 {
      padding: 40px 80px;
    }

    .section-m1 {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    body {
      width: 100%;
    }

    #header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 80px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      z-index: 999;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
    }

    #navbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    #navbar li {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    #navbar li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      transition: 0.3 ease;
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 5%;
    }

    #navbar li a:hover,
    #navbar li a.active {
      color: #088178;
    }

    #navbar li a.active ::after{
      content: "";
      width: 30%;
      height: 2px;
      background: #888178;
      bottom: -4px;
      position: absolute;
      left: 20px;
    }

    .cover {
      background-image: url(img/pic2.jpg);
      background-position: center;
      background-size: cover;
      position: relative;
      height: 815px;
      width: 100%;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

    .course {
      width: 80%;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 100px;
    }

    .row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 5%;
    }

    .course-col {
      flex-basis: 31%;
      background: #ecf9f2;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 5%;
      padding: 20px 12px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .course-col img{
      height: 50px;
      width: 50px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin-left: 200px;
    }

    h3 {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .boxContainer {
      margin: auto;
      margin-top: 2%;
      position: relative;
      width: 300px;
      height: 42px;
      border: 2px solid #2980b9;
      padding: 0px 10px;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }

    .elementsContainer {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .search {
      border: none;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0px 5px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      color: #424242;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    #header img{
      height: 100px;
      width: 100px;
    }

    .search:focus {
      outline: none;
    }

    .fa-magnifying-glass {
      font-size: 26;
      color: #2980b9;
    }

    .course-col:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: 1s;
    }

    .footer {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 0;
    }

    .icon .fa-brands {
      color: #f44336;
      margin: 0 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }

    .info p{
      top: 468px;
      position: relative;
      margin-left: 129px;
      color: rgb(250, 246, 246)
    }

    .cover h2{
      top: 448px;
      position: relative;
      margin-left: 129px;
      color: rgb(236, 247, 235);
      font-size: 95px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .featured-card {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  

  <section class="cover">
    <h2>Green Leaves</h2>
    <div class="info">
      <p>
        Welcome!! to Green Leaves. Explore more to find Fresh products.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="course">
    <h1>Top Products</h1>
    <p>Few of the Products are Listed Below.</p>

    <div class="boxContainer">
      <table class="elementsContainer">
        <tr>
          <td>
            <input type="text" class="search" placeholder="Enter Products.">
          </td>
          <td>
            <a href="#"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="course-col">
        <img src="/img/apple2.jpg" alt="">
        <h3>Apple</h3>
        <p>Our carefully curated selection of vegetables includes a wide variety of greens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="course-col">
        <img src="/img/banana.jpg" alt="">
        <h3>Banana</h3>
        <p>Our carefully curated selection of vegetables includes a wide variety of greens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="course-col">
        <img src="/img/grapes.jpg" alt="">
        <h3>Grapes</h3>
        <p>Our carefully curated selection of vegetables includes a wide variety of greens.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="course">
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="course-col">
        <h3>Free Home Delivery</h3>
        <p>Our carefully curated selection of vegetables includes a wide variety of greens, roots, and seasonal
          delights, handpicked to meet your culinary needs and preferences.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="course-col">
        <h3>Return Services**</h3>
        <p>we prioritize quality and freshness above all else. Our team of expert farmers and quality control
          specialists work tirelessly to ensure that each vegetable meets our stringent standards.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="course-col">
        <h3>Daily New Offer</h3>
        <p>With our user-friendly website, you can easily browse our extensive range of vegetables, select your
          favorites, and place your order in just a few clicks.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  


</body>

</html>